= Randall Paints

Randall Paints is a physicist specializing in astrodynamics. He was recruited by the Luminous Outreach Department in 2048 after an individual who studied his work put his name forward. The Luminous government later discovered his research into sensor data anomalies, which he accredits to organic or civilisational interference.